{"tid":1640533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[定性] 既然政府/親政府定性我地暴動，點解我地唔定性番對方","createTime":"2019-10-09T04:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T12:01:16.000Z","uid":126283,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"57453adb840d0f3acb27e57e77e4fe7175bac8aa","tid":1640533,"uid":126283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"政府:<br />\n612 - 已被定性為<span style=\"color: red;\">暴動/ riot</span><br />\n1001 - 已被定性為<span style=\"color: red;\">暴動/ riot</span><br />\n<br />\n咁同樣我地都可以聲明:<br />\n721 - Pro-govt gang members made a <span style=\"color: red;\">terrorist attack</span> at Yuen Long Station<br />\n831 - Hong Kong Police Force made a <span style=\"color: red;\">terrorist attack</span> at Prince Edward Station<br />\n1006 - A pro-govt taxi driver made a <span style=\"color: red;\">terrorist attack</span><br />\n<br />\n對方既然用暴動定性我地，點解唔同佢鬥定性，尤其向外國表示政府/親政府用乜方法處理佢地眼中既麻煩<br />\n咁當然字眼不能亂用，所以應該集中喺比較少異議既事件，而呢啲事件既共通點係對大量人士造成傷害/潛在傷害<br />\n<br />\n磚:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OgfM644.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOgfM644.png&h=818a80e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要向外國說明佢地就係一班支持<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恐怖主義</span></strong></span>既人物，係<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恐怖份子</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n咁當然唔一定要下下都用恐襲字眼，用一個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>貼切既字詞定性佢地既行為</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"aeff9af39285c0224bf947f0c2b0022ae19ec01a","tid":1640533,"uid":293816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:03:17.000Z","msg":"香港人 反抗！"},{"pid":"655dd90e1699c59b6fea81587bf0b2c19eba68e4","tid":1640533,"uid":69741,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T04:03:50.000Z","msg":"因為無人理你個定性，even民間記者會喺主流媒體之中既主流，tvb上面既曝光率都唔高<br />\n你個定性傳播範圍有限，最後可能都只係喺同溫層傳播"},{"pid":"ff337acca07813856e4462